# App purpose :
platform for collecting travel expense reprots from employees

# Main interface :
Company Admin creates trip data (all mandatory, besides comments):
  departure date
  return date
  trip purpose
  list of names of employees who participated the trip
  list of countries visited
  comments

  system assigns trip number, prefix + 4digit running number

any user :
  log into one of the trips of the compay he chose at login, and add expense details to the trip
  each expnse detials has the following data:
    date (not mandatory)
    amount
    currency
    description/vendor
    expense type
    
  

system screens:
  login (+choose company, if user is associated with multiple companies)
  list of trips , with filters (+add new trip)
  
login with email, or google account, or MS account
sys admin :
  new company (+admin user, prefix for trip numbers)
  new trip
  new expense type

company admin :
  new user
  disable user

action log

reports:
activity log
expense reports to employee (only his expenses in all the trips in all the companies)

